measurements.description: Two flowers and one bud on one 37-cm arched inflorescence; dorsal sepal undulate, hirsute exterior, cream overlaid green medially, striped cordovan proximally; synsepal undulate, hirsute exterior, green; petals narrow, twisted distally, undulate, ciliate, light green blotched cordovan; pouch cream overlaid rose, speckled darker rose; staminode dark olive green; substance firm; texture matte.
